nd not recognized who his father.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The police said if Tanya is not recognized, acknowledge it inadequate, but the child will take. Then she admitted. Conducted new DNA examination, which confirmed that it is - a cousin Tanya Ostap. He was 14 years old. He is - the son of my brother Michael on first marriage &quot;- said the mother of the schoolgirl.<br />\n<br />\nOstap with his mother and her roommate live in Borislav. According to the boy, they Tatiana seen enough adult movies online.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11歲女大肚告錯鄰居 上真人騷揭經手人係阿哥定繼父<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/446345/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/446345/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d6dac105b9c52117138de3f7c677d257d388734c","tid":554583,"uid":62409,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T16:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6fu35Aq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6fu35Aq.gif&h=247f708e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9b6f896566fdb538e9d32658058a725abaaf4a4","tid":554583,"uid":59611,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6dac105b9c52117138de3f7c677d257d388734c","tid":554583,"uid":62409,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T16:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6fu35Aq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6fu35Aq.gif&h=247f708e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T16:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243d8061907cfd1daf8326aa7338482fe5d39806","tid":554583,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T16:53:01.000Z","msg":"結果仲未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"3059670c04ec1a00920d9103a718be1164cbb070","tid":554583,"uid":3883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"243d8061907cfd1daf8326aa7338482fe5d39806","tid":554583,"